      The Glenn Beck Program - 02/19/14Wednesday, February 19, 2014 10:27 AM




Glenn tells the tale of any parent's worst nightmare
 and what you can do to help Justina.

  Also, Lou Pelletier, father of Justina Pelletier,

  Plus, Mike Rowe joins Glenn in the NYC studio to talk about hard work and passion.
